      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a fantastic vehicle that's been truly well-cared for! This car is in good condition, offering a smooth drive and a clean, inviting interior that shows it's been a priority for its previous owner. It\u2019s a reliable and solid choice for anyone looking for a quality ride that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure!",
