    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is currently non-running. The engine requires a complete rebuild or replacement to be roadworthy again. While the exterior shows significant wear and the interior needs a deep cleaning and repair, the frame remains solid, making it a potential candidate for a dedicated restoration project or a valuable source of spare parts. Please expect to tow this vehicle from its current location.",
